Description:
Family Home With Lots To Offer
This three bedroom brick veneer residence is sited on a generous 847 square metre corner block providing easy caravan/ boat access to shed and fully fenced yard.
The renovated kitchen has stainless-steel wall oven, cook top, rangehood, pot draw, dishwasher and breakfast bar. The kitchen opens to the separate meals area with adjoining good sized lounge that has a solid fuel heater and sliding doors opening to outdoor entertaining area. The second spacious living area also opens to the outdoor area and could ideally be used for a parents retreat or rumpus room. All bedrooms with built-in-robes and ceiling fans; generous size main with ensuite.
This home showcases an impressive outdoor area with built-in bar and a pot belly heater suitable for all year round enjoyment for family and friends.
Excellent car accommodation with double carport under roofline, double carport in rear yard and a lock up garage with concrete flooring and power.
An excellent home with lots to offer!

Description:
Retirement Living
Positioned in Oasis Village this three bedroom home has been lovingly cared for and is quite generous in size. The open plan living has kitchen overlooking a separate meals and a spacious lounge looking out over the water. The kitchen has a corner pantry, gas stove and ample cupboard space. Two bedrooms have built in robes with the master bedroom enjoying a walk through robe into its own ensuite. Both the ensuite and bathroom both have a shower, vanity and toilet. Climate is controlled by reverse cycle split systems, gas heater and ceiling fan in the lounge and master bedroom has a ceiling fans as well. Externally there is a garage with remote control access, outdoor entertaining area, garden shed and deck overlooking the water. This home offers quality fixtures and fittings throughout and is well worth an inspection. Oasis Village is set in beautiful landscaped surrounds and gives retirees the freedom and independence they deserve. Facilities include in-ground swimming pool, tennis court, recreational hall and so much more. It is conveniently located less than 2km from the CBD and has walking tracks directly into town and also has public bus transport coming through on a regular basis.

Description:
3 Minutes To Town - 3 Acres - 3 Bedroom
This spacious three bedroom home is a rare find. Situated only three minutes from the Cobram township on three acres.
Featuring a spacious kitchen, with plenty of cupboard and bench space. Good sized breakfast bar, wall oven, gas cook top and timber look vinyl flooring. The kitchen overlooks the dining/ meals area. Large lounge room with study nook. Three good sized bedrooms all with carpet and built-in-robes. Main bathroom with plenty of cupboard space under vanity.
Ducted evaporative cooling throughout and reverse cycle split system in lounge room.
Huge rumpus/ games room adjoined to the home with toilet facilities with lots of potential. Direct house access from double lock up garage.
Great sized 12m x 10m shed/ workshop with concrete flooring and power. Excellent veggie garden with watering system. Stock and domestic bore and excellent paddocks for pets or stock.
Enjoy a rural lifestyle so close to town. Call today to book a private inspection!

Description:
Your Next Family Home!
This three bedroom family home plus study offers two generous sized living areas. The kitchen which has an abundance of bench space and cupboards and also has an electric cooktop, underbench oven and dishwasher. It overlooks the separate meals and family room and opens onto a large outdoor entertaining area. The master bedroom is located to the front of the home with walk in robe and ensuite with the remaining two bedrooms located to the rear, both with built in robes. They share the family bathroom with bath, shower and vanity. The study opens onto the second living space and could be utilised as a fourth bedroom. The home has ducted gas heating and evaporative air conditioning. Externally there is a garden shed and double garage which is open at the back making it ideal for those who love to entertain as it makes a fantastic extension to the outdoor entertaining area. For the investor, this property was previously being rented at $390 per week. This home offers low maintenance gardens in a sought after area of town and must be inspected to appreciate what is on offer.
